reviews.review_text: Good Show / Good Aud Recording This show is a fun show. The recording is clean and a little more crips than the Vernon recording.
Better than a 4 The best shows in this run of course get a 5, but all things considered, I'm giving this recording a 5 to up the average to 4+.
